data.description: The home is situated down a long driveway off the road and has 16x20 shed to boot and an old tractor shed for storing needs. 2 bedroom 2 bath set up. Covered carport/ outside entertainment area. Part of the carport is also enclosed with a half bath and the laundry room.  All this located on a 255 foot above sea level ridge. Metal Roof and New Central Heat installed in October 2020.
